Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:37.50,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:91295,97509}{\i1}Nozomi, deeply plunged in debt,\Nwas offered a contract by DM productions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:40.09,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:97509,100095}{\i1}for a sum of 300,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:44.14,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:100095,104141}{\i1}At that time, Egawa Isao was traveling\Nin Europe and Fanni had left for America.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:49.02,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:104141,109021}{\i1}Having no one around to advise her, Nozomi\Nsigned the contract without much thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:54.44,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:109021,114443}{\i1}Soon after, DM Productions sent\NNozomi on a tour in the Tōhoku region.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:02:00.69,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:114610,120699}{\fad(1000,1000)}— Episode 11 —\NThe Golden Trumpet{NOTE:第11話\\Nひびけ！トランペット}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:17.75,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:133253,137758}One, two, three, four…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:21.01,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:137758,141011}Okay. Looks like we have everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:25.43,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:141011,145432}I think the time has come\Nto introduce you, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:27.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:145432,147559}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:29.10,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:147559,149102}Attention, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:33.06,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:149102,153065}I would like to introduce you to a new\Nsinger full of promise, Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.94,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:153065,155943}Here, greet your new companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:155943,157444}Hello, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:39.32,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:157444,159321}Hello, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:40.36,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:159321,160364}Here is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:160364,162074}…Hoshimura Sachiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:45.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:162074,165369}Your "Southern Woman"\Nis very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:46.41,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:165369,166411}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:49.99,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:166411,169998}But compared to the gentlemen sitting\Nnext to me, my successes are nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:52.37,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:169998,172376}Speaking of whom,\Nhe's Mizushima Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:55.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:172376,175462}You won the grand prize for your\N"Farewell In The Morning".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:58.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:175462,178632}I saw the movie, too.\NI was deeply moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:00.63,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:179383,180634}By the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:02.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:181218,182261}No. Your song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:06.09,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:182261,186098}Hmm. By the way, I heard\Nyou were a student of Egawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:08.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:186098,188600}You know Mr. Egawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:12.39,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:188600,192396}Yes, for a long time.\NWe're like brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:16.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:192396,196608}Really? If you don't mind, then,\NI'd like to ask you for something later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.56,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:196608,198569}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:22.15,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:198569,202155}We just improvised a few songs\Ntogether. It was nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:27.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:203115,207953}I want to sing songs that will move\Neveryone who hears them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:207953,209788}I won't stand for anything less.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:38.67,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:214209,218672}Looks like you've got everything you need.\NWhat do you think, Nicchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.22,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:226430,228223}Do you know who that man is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:48.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:228223,228890}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:54.39,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:228890,234396}I can't blame you. You were wearing diapers\Nwhen the Japanese Jazz Festival was held.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:59.19,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:234396,239192}He's the first Japanese who took the crown\Nof the best trumpeter. He's that Nicchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:00.52,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:239192,240527}Nicchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.27,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:240527,242279}Yes. Also known as Nitta Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:03.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:242279,243155}Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:07.99,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:243155,247993}Yes, he had a lot of talent, but unfortunately\Nit all got drowned in alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.20,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:247993,250203}Ain't that right, Nicchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:14.95,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:250203,254958}Why do you pull out those past stories\Nto this kid who can't tell right from left?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:27.55,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:262799,267554}Drunken or not, when my lips touch the trumpet,\Nthey can still make some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:30.97,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:267554,270974}That pretty much sums it up, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:37.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:272434,277481}{\i1}"Drunken or not, when my lips touch the trumpet,\Nthey can still make some money"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:42.11,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{TIME:278523,282110}We will stop for five minutes at the Aomori\NStation to let an express train through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:282110,284404}Mister…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.48,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:284404,285489}What? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:48.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:286698,288200}Uhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.74,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:288200,289743}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.41,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:291828,294414}Is that all there is to music to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:55.54,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:294414,295540}Music… what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:05:00.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:297709,300212}I'm talking about\Nwhat you've told me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:02.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:300212,302881}That it's good as long as\Nit earns you money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:05.92,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:303840,305926}Damn right it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:07.84,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:305926,307844}What else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:307844,309012}A lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:309012,310597}Music is about passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:13.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:310597,313183}If you put your heart into it,\Nyou'll move other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:19.52,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:316436,319523}Let me ask you.\NSo what if it moves them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:22.23,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:319523,322234}That alone won't buy you\Na single bottle of scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:322234,323568}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:27.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:323568,327155}I think that kind of attitude\Nis an insult to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:28.99,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:328240,328990}Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:330367,332494}Excuse me.
