Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:26.06,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:383311,386064}Hey, girl!\NYou're good, you know!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.48,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:386064,387482}I was kinda moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:31.44,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:387482,391445}Good! More!\NEncore, encore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:34.44,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:391445,394448}You hear the grandma!\NSing us another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:36.40,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:394448,396408}It was pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:40.37,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:396408,400370}You got that right, man!\NHow will it be, girl?
