Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.58,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:409296,410589}Way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.92,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:410589,411923}Congrats, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.25,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:411923,414259}Wait, wait. There's still more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:57.34,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:414259,417345}"At that moment,\Nwithout even a single reflector,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:07:00.76,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:417345,420766}it seemed to me like\Nthe most beautiful stage in the world".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.18,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:420766,422184}I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:05.27,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:422184,425270}Everything is going\Nfor the best for our Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:09.27,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:425270,429274}She's surprisingly fine\Nall by herself in the adult world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:10.44,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:429274,430442}You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:11.61,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:430442,431610}Same goes to you, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.07,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:431610,434070}Oh, you noticed?\NSharp girl, haha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:19.82,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:435864,439826}Alright then, as her number one fan,\NI should be by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.36,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:439826,441369}I'll go and see her live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.49,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:441369,442496}Ah, the sky's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:24.58,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:442496,444581}Sis is looking at it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:29.60,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:446333,449603}– Nozomi!\N– Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:42.55,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:458094,462557}{\fad(0,2000)}Mine Nozomi{NOTE:水島タケシ\\N青葉フレッシュ大行進\\N星村さちこ\\N峰のぞみ\\NPMプロダクション}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:36.05,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:450378,456051}{\fad(2000,0)\fnArial}♪{\fn}  …soon enough will go by  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:44.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:456051,464142}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Grin when you're feeling good  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:嬉しい時はニヤニヤしよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:53.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:464142,473568}{\fad(0,2000)\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Whistle when you're having fun.  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:楽しい時は口笛を吹こう}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:06.95,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:485163,486957}N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:10.37,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:486957,490377}If we give more songs to Mine-kun,\Nwe have to them from someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.54,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:490961,492546}Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.75,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:493171,495757}You always have\Nto satisfy the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:18.09,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:495757,498093}That's the basic foundation\Nof the professional world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:20.47,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:498093,500470}Starting tomorrow, you'll have\Nmore spotlight, Mine-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:21.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:500470,501471}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:501471,503723}But I'm just a beginner…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:27.26,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:503723,507269}She's right. I'm the award-winning\NMizushima Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:29.72,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:507269,509729}There is this thing called pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:33.14,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:509729,513149}Sorry, but pride\Ndoesn't make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:36.44,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:513608,516444}I'm expecting a lot from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.74,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:519656,521741}I'm sorry. A mere beginner like me—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:44.53,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:521741,524536}You don't need to\Napologize to us, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:46.74,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:524536,526746}But Mizu-chan is right.\NWe have our dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:52.79,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:528832,532794}When someone new steals your popularity,\Nyou do everything to take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:55.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:533336,535338}Hoshimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:58.04,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:535338,538049}Let's go to town\Nfor a drink, Mizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:545891,547601}That's Nitta-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:14.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:553064,554816}Looks like he tries\Nto compose something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:03.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:597484,603114}{\i1}Nozomi's passionate attitude continued\Nto capture her audience's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:08.70,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:603114,608703}{\i1}Day by day, she was growing more and more\Nas DM Productions' most vibrant star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:14.62,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:608703,614626}{\i1}No matter where she went,\Nthe audience cheered to Nozomi's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:18.88,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:614626,618880}{\i1}But it wasn't just the audience\Nwho was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:23.92,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:618880,623927}{\i1}Thank you, Nozomi.\NI'm going to squeeze the life out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:32.81,Default,Random person,0,0,0,,{TIME:631601,632811}Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.98,Default,Random person,0,0,0,,{TIME:632811,634980}It's good to see you back, Mr. Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.27,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:634980,636272}Thank you for coming to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:37.44,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:636272,637440}Let me take your baggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:39.02,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:637440,639025}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:40.36,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:639025,640360}Sune-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.44,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:640360,641444}Where's Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:43.53,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:641444,643530}Ah, about that, you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:46.24,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:643530,646241}Oh, Nozomi went on a tour\Nto the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:48.74,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:647033,648743}What? What tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:53.79,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:649119,653790}She has written a letter and\Ninstructed me to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:56.25,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:653790,656251}To apologize for working\Nfor DM Productions, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:59.12,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:656918,659129}DM? Did you say\NDM Productions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:01.21,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:659129,661214}Y-Yes, it's DM Productions…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:08.17,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:665802,668179}That stupid kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.22,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:668179,669222}Master…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.72,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:670265,671725}She's expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.35,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:674853,676354}{\i1}This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.89,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:676354,678898}{\i1}This is your end, Nozomi.
Comment: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:22.76,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:682769,682769}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:30.26,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:685096,690268}Now I just have to find out\Nwhere she's singing. Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:38.69,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:696274,698693}Oh, alright. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:41.69,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:699986,701696}Found it! This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:47.20,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:703323,707202}Let's see… "Mine Nozomi".\NI can't see her name anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.41,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:709371,712415}Hey, hey, hey!\NGet me the guy in charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.29,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:712415,713291}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:56.46,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:713291,716461}Not "huh", call your manager.\NCall your manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.17,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,{TIME:716461,719172}Y-Yes sir, I'm the manager.\NHow can I be of help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:02.80,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:719172,722801}Where did you hide Nozomi-chan?\NWhere is Nozomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.34,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,{TIME:722801,724344}Nozomi-chan who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:05.92,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:724344,725929}You little…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:08.76,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:725929,728765}Mine Nozomi. The one who was\Nsupposed to sing here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:11.22,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,{TIME:728765,731226}Ah, the one with\Nthe DM Productions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:12.81,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:731226,732811}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.52,Default,Manager,0,0,0,,{TIME:732811,735522}She extended her stay\Nfor 2 days in Asamushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.23,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:735522,737232}Extended her stay?\NIn Asamushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:35.75,Default,Important guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:751371,755750}Thanks to Mine-kun the theater is full tonight.\NHow about doing a double show, Sasaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:38.79,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:755750,758795}I don't mind,\Nif that's what you wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:42.13,Default,Important guy,0,0,0,,{TIME:758795,762132}Absolutely. I've heard\Na newcomer sing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:44.05,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:762132,764050}Thank you for your kind words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:53.60,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:770348,773601}– That sounds pretty bad.\N– Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.86,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:780150,781860}Hoshimura, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:03.15,Default,Hoshimura Sachiko,0,0,0,,{TIME:781860,783153}In a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:06.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:784696,786322}Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:09.53,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:786322,789534}Yes, Nozomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:12.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:789534,792495}I'm sorry, but could you please\Ncut my time a little bit short?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.95,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:792495,793955}Cut it short?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:15.58,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:793955,795582}It's out of question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:18.29,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:795582,798293}Actually, we were offered\Na double show today just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:22.33,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:798293,802338}But I was worried about your overwork,\Nso I've already reduced your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:803381,805258}But I have a bad cough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:29.59,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:805258,809596}A little cough never killed anybody.\NDo gargling with water and salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:32.43,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:809596,812432}Mizushima-san, you're up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:35.14,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:812432,815143}I know. Why do you think\NI'm putting my shoes on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:40.52,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:816853,820523}There's a second performance tonight.\NDon't forget that it's not a school play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:47.28,Default,Random person,0,0,0,,{TIME:826237,827280}We're so done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.94,Default,Random person,0,0,0,,{TIME:827280,828948}Let's go drink something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.74,Default,Mizushima Takeshi,0,0,0,,{TIME:828948,830742}Hey, don't leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.54,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:834370,837540}Your face doesn't say so,\Nbut you're quite a hypocrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:58.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:837540,838708}A hypocrite?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.66,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:840502,841669}Yes, a hypocrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:06.96,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:841669,846966}I'm talking about how you asked\Nto sing less songs tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:10.55,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:846966,850553}Whereas my worldview\Nwas supposedly so corrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:11.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:850553,851888}How's that related?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:17.47,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:853264,857477}First you preach to me about\Nmoving people by singing from your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:21.89,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:857477,861898}Now you don't want to sing\Njust because you have a little sore throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:29.65,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:866194,869656}If you sing with your heart,\Nthen what do you need throat for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.03,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:873618,876037}If you weren't so arrogant,\Nwere more humble,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:39.16,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:876037,879165}you'd sing no matter what\Nand gain the experience you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:45.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:882001,885088}Does it mean my words\Nhad effect on you, Nitta-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.29,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:885088,886297}No. You're still green.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:55.78,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:894389,895782}Wanna give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:15:01.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:896099,901646}{\fad(500,0)\fnArial}♪{\fn}  You may remember,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I wonder,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:君はおぼえているかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:07.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:901646,907944}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  the white swing.  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:君はおぼえているかしら\\Nあの白いブランコ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:13.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:907944,913866}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  We sat in together,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  swayed by the wind.  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:風に吹かれてふたりでゆれた}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:19.58,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:913866,919581}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  The white swing,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あの白いブランコ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:25.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:919581,925461}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  if still unbroken,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  will let me embrace  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:まだこわれずにあるのなら}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:31.71,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:925461,931718}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  your look at that time  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  that lives in my memory  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:君の面影抱きしめて}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:37.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:931718,937348}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  and let me get on it alone, I wonder.  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:ひとりでゆれてみようかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:47.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:937348,947233}{\fad(0,1000)\fnArial}♪{\fn}  The swing at that time, now far away,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  was immaculately pure white.  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:遠いあの日の白い白い白いブランコ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:54.44,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:952155,954449}Hurry up and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:03.04,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:959829,963041}Don't exert yourself\Ntoday, Mine-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:963041,964542}Manager…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:07.50,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:964542,967503}It's fine. That little cough\Ndoesn't matter, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:967503,968963}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.67,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:968963,971674}You have to admit\Nthat our pay is very generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:15.67,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:971674,975678}Complaints about headaches\Nor stomach aches are really out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:18.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:975678,978556}But I still haven't got paid yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:22.64,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:978556,982644}You'll be paid after the tour.\NThat's how things work in the show business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:26.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:982644,986939}But that's not what we agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:29.31,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:986939,989317}Well, you can leave\Nwhenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:29.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:989317,989901}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:34.69,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:990943,994697}I didn't want to tell you this\Nto avoid disappointing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:38.53,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:994697,998534}But I'll have you know that you have\Nnothing in Tōkyō to go back to anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:998534,1000244}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:43.58,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000244,1003581}Do you know what your mentor\Nhas said at the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:47.33,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003581,1007335}That he doesn't need a student who does\Nwhatever she pleases, and that he expels you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007335,1008336}Expels?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:49.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008336,1009504}He expelled me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.71,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009504,1010713}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:55.38,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010713,1015385}So if you do not commit yourself\Nseriously to this tour and your fans here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:57.13,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015385,1017136}you will become nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:05.35,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022809,1025353}Whoa, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.56,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026604,1029565}I missed her so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:15.08,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032652,1035088}I'm here for you, Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:19.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036614,1039075}{\i1}Mr. Egawa has expelled me…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:32.58,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050086,1052588}{\i1}Mr. Egawa…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:39.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055842,1059512}{\i1}Mr. Egawa has expelled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:48.18,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064851,1068187}{\i1}You're expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:53.44,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070898,1073443}What are you doing, kid?\NWe can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:18:00.49,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076446,1080491}{\i1}Nozomi-chan, what's wrong?\NWhat happened to the results of our rehearsal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:04.20,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080783,1084203}– Get a grip!\N– What are you just standing there for!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.95,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084203,1086956}Hey, buddy!\NGot a problem with Nozomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:08.04,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086956,1088040}Get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:09.29,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088040,1089292}I'll take over from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:14.75,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091377,1094756}If you don't like it,\Nget the hell out, punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:15.88,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094756,1095882}Understood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101053,1102305}Nitta-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:30.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108686,1110813}It's the song he composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.15,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115860,1118154}What a sudden change!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:41.65,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118154,1121657}I like it! Way to go, trumpet guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121657,1123659}What a fabulous solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:52.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129874,1132385}Thank you, Nitta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:57.34,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135963,1137340}The heck you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:59.75,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137340,1139759}Hands off me.\NI was only protecting art!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:01.01,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139759,1141010}I'm innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:08.47,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145139,1148476}I think we're going to have\Nto set up a new contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:14.35,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151312,1154357}But I don't mean to overlook\Nwhat has happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:17.40,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154357,1157401}Also, I'm afraid you're stuck with us\Nif you want to succeed in this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:23.36,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160154,1163366}Our new offer is 150,000.\NAs for the payment…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:27.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163366,1167286}This isn't right.\NI need those 300,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:29.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167286,1169789}I promise I'll work\Neven harder from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:33.45,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169789,1173459}Don't shout like that.\NYou have a sore throat, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:36.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173459,1176963}I'm begging you. Manager…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:39.75,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176963,1179757}Give the girl what\Nshe asks for, Sasaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:42.00,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179757,1182009}We're having an important discussion.\NDon't disturb us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:44.09,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182009,1184095}Oh, yeah, I can see that, Sasaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:49.10,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184095,1189100}First you ruin her throat, then reduce her pay,\Nnow you scold her. Really, way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.93,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189100,1190935}Are you drunk again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:53.81,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191686,1193813}No. I'm perfectly sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:56.35,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193813,1196357}You ungrateful bastard!\NWanna get fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.81,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196357,1198818}You're firing me? What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:19:59.44,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198818,1199443}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:01.94,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199443,1201946}You can't fire me. I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:03.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201946,1203447}Nitta-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:08.87,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205491,1208870}I won't ask you for compensation.\NBut I can't let you rip Nozomi-chan off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.20,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208870,1210204}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:11.83,Default,Sasaya,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210204,1211831}A-Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:15.20,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211831,1215209}Don't change the contract and give her\Nthe whole 300,000 she deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:23.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221173,1223134}Nitta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:35.77,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231934,1235771}When you talked about how music\Nis about your heart, I got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:38.64,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235771,1238649}At my age I should know better,\Nyet I reacted with hostility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:45.15,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241319,1245156}Sorry that I forced you to sing before,\Ndespite knowing you have a sore throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246073,1247325}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:51.32,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247325,1251329}At that time, I had only\None desire, to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:53.49,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251329,1253497}But you were stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:58.66,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253497,1258669}Moreover, you reminded me that I was\Nlike you once, and music was all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:06.30,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261047,1266302}The reason why I've decided to leave was\Nto start over and become like Satchmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:09.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266302,1269889}Satchmo? You mean the famous\Ntrumpeter, Louis Armstrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:12.93,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269889,1272934}Yes. I want to get back to jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:16.39,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272934,1276395}Even if I earn less,\NI will definitely be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:20.94,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276395,1280942}Thank you. You saved me and made me\Nrediscover the purity of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:23.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280942,1283194}You're giving me too much credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:25.69,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283194,1285696}This is my farewell gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:29.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287239,1289408}It's the melody you composed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.24,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289408,1290242}You knew about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:32.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290242,1292328}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:34.70,Default,Nitta Aki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292328,1294705}You better sever your ties\Nwith DM quickly as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:52.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309261,1312515}Good bye, Nitta-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:18.58,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334578,1338582}{\i1}A trumpeter overflowing\Nwith a great talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:22.92,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338582,1342920}{\i1}Nitta Akira, who was like\Na whirlwind in the jazz world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:27.84,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342920,1347842}{\i1}The passion for the music\Nthat he was about to lose was revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:33.01,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347842,1353014}{\i1}It was all thanks to one girl, Mine Nozomi\Nand her passion for the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:39.97,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353014,1359979}{\i1}On the other hand, for Nozomi,\Nmeeting another person struggling with life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:44.81,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1359979,1364817}{\i1}gave her insight as to what the path\Nto becoming a professional singer looks like.
Comment: 0,0:23:04.60,0:23:04.60,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1384603,1384603}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:11.51,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1387048,1391510}{\i1}During her local performances,\NMine Nozomi's voice
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:15.59,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1391510,1395598}{\i1}was deeply ingrained in the minds\Nof people in these unfamiliar places.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:19.81,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1395598,1399810}{\i1}However, her manager, who knew\Nher ability to capture crowds
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.81,0:23:25.35,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1399810,1405357}{\i1}made Nozomi sing day and night,\Nwithout a moment to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:28.27,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1405357,1408277}{\i1}While Nozomi's outstanding talent\Nwas given more spotlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:34.20,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1408277,1414200}{\i1}it resulted in reducing the song count\Nfor the former star, Hoshimura Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:37.99,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1414200,1417995}{\i1}Nozomi is met with jealousy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:41.54,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1417995,1421540}{\i1}Continuing her journey in this state,\Nwhile struggling and suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.54,0:23:47.50,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1421540,1427505}{\i1}eventually Nozomi's throat gave in\Nto the point she was no longer able to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.63,0:23:53.88,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1427630,1433886}{\i1}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"Don't Cry, Dear".
